78#define ALLOC(X, N) (X) = calloc((N), sizeof(*(X)))
79
80typedef struct {
81 MechTypeList initiator_mech_types;
82 gss_OID preferred_mech_type;
83 gss_OID negotiated_mech_type;
84 gss_ctx_id_t negotiated_ctx_id;
85 OM_uint32 mech_flags;
86 OM_uint32 mech_time_rec;
87 gss_name_t mech_src_name;
88 unsigned int open : 1;
89 unsigned int local : 1;
90 unsigned int require_mic : 1;
91 unsigned int verified_mic : 1;
92 unsigned int maybe_open : 1;
93 HEIMDAL_MUTEX ctx_id_mutex;
94
95 gss_name_t target_name;
96
97 u_char oidbuf[17];
98 size_t oidlen;
99
100} *gssspnego_ctx;
101
102typedef struct {
103 gss_OID_desc type;
104 gss_buffer_desc value;
105 gss_name_t mech;
106} *spnego_name;
